{"tid":448073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想同佢前男友有任何比較","createTime":"2017-10-26T01:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T10:23:53.000Z","uid":82786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c71b6b5c28351616e32e50215943811ee1973b4c","tid":448073,"uid":82786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"一個月之前同ex散咗<br />\n同佢其實識咗好耐 但之後先一齊<br />\n所以我好清楚佢啲感情經歷<br />\n知佢好鐘意佢ex嗰一類型嘅男人<br />\n其實我本身都係嗰一種style <br />\n但我feel到ex對佢前男友好似仲有種依戀<br />\n我真係好唔想活係佢前男友個影子之下<br />\n所以反而改變咗我自己<br />\n結果ex反而唔鐘意 但又冇同我講<br />\n慢慢累積落黎 最後都係分咗手<br />\n但我一直都唔夠膽同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜自己仲係外國 咩都挽救唔到<br />\n嗰種感覺真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好後悔"},{"pid":"7ec78c174109d9db528e9b118f44565d03ab987b","tid":448073,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"189f5e54b7b654dbece928a544b113a430ef7f44","tid":448073,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"佢當你水泡姐"},{"pid":"104aa79562b5b2cb1f78efe9fe9d187b084e177f","tid":448073,"uid":82786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢當你水泡姐</blockquote><br />\n又唔係嘅 呢樣我清楚 佢真係有鐘意過我"},{"pid":"f3998feaa07bc1b19b3032880a0e657d07c0f810","tid":448073,"uid":82786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"唉 依家諗起都覺得自己好撚on 9<br />\n好撚後悔<br />\n偏偏又唔想同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明大家一開始係互相鐘意大家<br />\n但就係因為自己大男人 唔想活係人地嘅影子